=======================================================================================
# Pathfinder RAT - Changelog
=======================================================================================
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased] - 3.0.0

## Testing 2.21.1 > 2.9.0

## [2.21.0] LATEST STABLE - 2023-11-24
### Added
- SS7 Protocol Stack > MTP Layer 6
- Keylogger functions

### Fixed
- Minor bug fixed

## [2.19.3] STABLE - 2021-12-10
### Fixed
- Minor bug fixed

## [2.19.1] STABLE - 2021-01-16
### Changed
- Front-end: minor layout adjustment

### Changed
- php
- mariadb server
- ss7 modules

## [2.16.4] STABLE - 2021-01-16
### Fixed
- Minor bug fixed

### Changed
- Payment method

## [2.16.2] STABLE - 2020-10-13
### Fixed
- Minor GUI layout bug fixed

### Added
- SS7 Protocol Stack > MTP Layer 5
- SS7 Protocol Stack > MTP Layer 4
- SIGTRAN Protocol Stack > MTP4

## [2.14] LATEST STABLE - 2020-05-06
### Changed
- SS7 MTP Layer 2 port

## [2.13.2 > 2.13.9] - 2020-05-02
### Changed
- Security fixes TLS > TOR

## [2.13.1] - 2020-02-21
### Added
- New visual identity.
- Version navigation bootstrap.
- Links to latest released version in previous versions.
- Keylogger functions
- File bootstrap assets/js/vendor/holder.min.js

## [2.13.0] BETA 2 - 2020-02-19
### Added
- Translation.
- Geo-location functions, also loaded bootstrap
- Media elements to folder library (svg, png, jpeg)

## [2.12.9] - 2020-02-18
### Changed
- Remove exclusionary mentions of "open source" since this project can
benefit both "open" and "closed" source projects equally.
- Improve argument against commit logs.

### Added
- Payload 3

## [2.12.0 > 2.12.7] - 2020-02-18
### Changed
- Update year to match in every section.
- Payload 2

### Fixed
- Fix typos in recent .pf file changes.
- Update outdated unreleased diff link.
- Payload 2

## [2.10.1 > 2.11.9] - 2020-02-15
### Added
- Links.
- Load new GUI: HTML, CSS, JavScript.
- Date format ISO 8601.
- Payload 1

### Changed
- Clarified section index.html > index.php.
- Duplicated sections index-1.php, index-2.php, index-3.php, index-4.php, index-5.php, index-6.php.
- Linux version becomes .AppImage, run on USB stick for better security.

## [2.10.0] - 2020-02-13
### Fixed
- Fix links to tag comparison URL with footnote-style links.
- Reading call logs history
- FUD variable

## [2.9.0 > 2.9.9] - 2020-01-19
### Changed
- Refer to a "change log" instead of a "CHANGELOG" throughout the site
to differentiate between the file and the purpose of the file â€” the
logging of changes.
- FUD variable

### Removed
- Remove empty sections from FRAMEWORK CLI, they occupy too much space and
create too much noise in the file.

## [2.8.0 > 2.8.9] - 2020-01-17
### Added
- Adding back-end variables and bootstrap GUI. 
- Execution functions to version tags on release headings.
- Unreleased section to gather unreleased changes.
- FUD functions

## [1.3.2 > 2.0.0] STARTING GUI DEVELOPMENT FOR PUBLIC RELEASE - 2019-12-18
### Added
- Database access AES 256 encryption.
- Variable for reverse-proxy HTTP calls and debugging.
- Backup functions
- App binder functions

## [1.0.1] - 2019-12-13
### Added
- CLI structure
- CHANGELOG.txt
